com.credenceid.biometrics

Class BiometricsManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.credenceid.biometrics.BiometricsManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Biometrics, BiometricDatabase, FaceEngine

    public class BiometricsManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements Biometrics, FaceEngine, BiometricDatabase
    This class provides access to Credence Biometrics features. To use, create an instance of this class in your activity. Override onActivityResult and pass the result to the BiometricsManager. 
    
 public class MyActivity extends Activity {
     // Maintain an instance of the BiometricsManager in your Activity
           BiometricsManager mBiometricsManager;
 }

 protected void onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState) {
     super.onCreate(savedInstanceState)
     // instantiate BiometricsManager in onCreate
     mBiometricsManager = new BiometricsManager(this);
     ...
 }

  protected void onActivityResult(int requestCode, int resultCode, Intent data) {
     // give BiometricsManager a chance to process onActivityResult
           mBiometricsManager.onActivityResult(requestCode, resultCode, data);
     ...
  }
